name: Reid
note:
Let planetary hours and days affect various aspects of your game:
Events: Make certain events only happen during specific planetary hours or days. For instance, a specific quest might only be available during a particular hour or day. 
Monsters/Enemies: Modify the behavior or appearance of creatures based on the current planetary time. 
NPCs: Control NPC behavior and dialogue based on the current planetary hour. 
Magic/Spells: Adjust the effectiveness of spells or the frequency of magic effects. 
Weather/Environment: Change the weather or scenery based on planetary time. 
Stats: Grant temporary stat bonuses or penalties based on the planetary hour or day.
